Module kivakit.microservice
Package com.telenav.kivakit.microservice

Class MicroserviceClusterMember<Data>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.microservice.MicroserviceClusterMember<Data>
Type Parameters:
Data - The type of user data for this member
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<MicroserviceClusterMember<Data>>
public class MicroserviceClusterMember<Data> extends Object implements Comparable<MicroserviceClusterMember<Data>>
Represents a member of a MicroserviceCluster with associated user data.

Properties

  • host() - The host where this member is running
  • processIdentifier() - The process on the host() where this member is running
  • data() - The user data for this member
  • isThis() - True if this member object is the one running in this process (on this host)

Leader Elections

When the MicroserviceCluster for this member loses a member or is joined by a new member, an election takes place to select a "leader". If this member is elected, elect(boolean) will be called with true, and the isLeader() method will return true. See MicroserviceCluster for details on elections.
